Question.Subject: What is lifemovesfastdontmissathing.com?
Question.Content:
I have heard this phrase, and now i came across this website, http://www.lifemovesfastdontmissathing.com/
What is it all about? all it says is "Life Moves Fast. Don't Miss a Thing." I don't get it! Can anyone explain?
Question.ChosenAnswer: It is about this commercial http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_1OHlFOee2w which is a great new phone which lets you run multiple apps at the same time. http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1abIXPwVBjo there is a link to a review of the phone.
